      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for libgcrypt fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2024-2236: timing-based side-channel flaw in RSA implementation can lead to decryption of RSA ciphertexts (bsc#1221107).\n",
